                    br
                    p We are asking ourselves these question all the time. It is a reality check, a reminder to upgrade skills, stay relevant and keep on top of modern technology. There will always be a dilemma of choosing the right reward for startup participants or any level employee. No approach is right or wrong, but let&rsquo;s review possible options.
